title: Jamie Dana: The Business Glow-Up
description: We're back with stylist and social media ninja, Jamie Dana! She is a hairstylist turned business owner and helps other stylists build a business and life they love using Instagram. She's kind of a big deal and has grown her brand through Youtube, Instagram, and online courses. She's dropping her knowledge here and letting us in on all her secrets to growing a thriving brand online!
